public class ContourLineAttributeDialog
extends javax.swing.JDialog

Edits a ContourLineAttribute. This dialog does not make a copy of the attribute so changes "Applied" will cause sgt to redraw the plot using the new properties unless batching has been turned on.

Example of ContourLineAttributeDialog use: 

 public void editCLAttribute(ContourLineAttribute cla) {
   ContourLineAttributeDialog clad = new ContourLineAttributeDialog();
   clad.showDialog(cla);
 }
